api_list.name: /converter/dmx/channelToDipSwitch
api_list.description: Convert a digital DMX channel (0-511) to the corresponding DIP switch settings (8 positions, 1/0)

required_parameters.name: dmxchannel
required_parameters.description: The numeral value of the LED channel (lowest possible channel 1, highest possible channel 511)

optional_parameters.name: reversehorizontally
optional_parameters.description: Switch horizontally between DIP switches from left to right (default: 12345678, reversed: 87654321)

optional_parameters.name: reversevertically
optional_parameters.description: Switch vertically between DIP switches from up to down (default: on/off, reversed: off/on)

api_list.name: /converter/dmx/dipSwitchToChannel
api_list.description: Convert the DIP switch settings (8 positions, 1/0) to the corresponding digital DMX channel (0-511)

required_parameters.name: dipswitch
required_parameters.description: The DIP switch value (8 positions 1/0)

optional_parameters.name: reversehorizontally
optional_parameters.description: Switch horizontally between DIP switches from left to right (default: 12345678, reversed: 87654321)

optional_parameters.name: reversevertically
optional_parameters.description: Switch vertically between DIP switches from up to down (default: on/off, reversed: off/on)
